 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b562bc92794c9485d4c709f18a8c7a44129f921","tid":166770,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bachelor 係 OU 拎，就算比你 taught master 入到 Poly City 又點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一黎 Taught master 係人都收，你入到唔代表你既水平比得上 Poly City Undergrad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n二黎你份 Resume 上面學歷一欄大大隻字寫住 OUHK，我想問洗到咩底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲人仲搞笑，諗住唔填 Bachelor 直接寫 Master <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗咁既說話都講得出，唔洗睇 resume 都知你智慧去到邊</blockquote><br />\n第一次完全認同你個post<br />\n不過可以加一樣野：如果入到ivy league/ oxbridge master的確洗到底嘅，係香港讀碩士，人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"aa4442a0891d6606f89ce16bd11407b805b93060","tid":166770,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>校園台某會然：ive--&gt;shitty（洗底不成）---&gt;hku(洗底)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話你入左開大就睇唔起你，至少你要努力求改變呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆 4 入八大有幾難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜班人只會揀舒舒服服繼續做廢物，廢得黎又唔想人地睇低佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就 FF 去八大洗底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆4不如retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b85516dd932e204c56ae7f2a642c52f68f5dd8","tid":166770,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明我都唔會睇低人，咁人人有長短處，你讀書唔叻，但<span style=\"color: red;\">有人脈識做人開公司</span>實搵得多過我呢個工程垃圾架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過絕對唔係呢班日日好食懶飛，鳩 hea 又怕人睇唔起，日日